// ===== INSTALLATION GUIDE =====
// How to set up the frontend with HashConnect

/*
1. Install dependencies:
   cd frontend
   npm install

2. Install HashPack wallet extension:
   - Chrome: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/hashpack/gjagmgiddbbciopjhllkdnddhcglnemk
   - Firefox: https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/hashpack/

3. Configure environment:
   cp .env.example .env
   # Edit .env with your contract addresses

4. Start development server:
   npm start

5. Connect wallet:
   - Open app in browser
   - Click "Connect HashPack"
   - Approve pairing in HashPack extension
   - Start using the app!

6. For production build:
   npm run build
   # Deploy build/ folder to your hosting
*/
